interview_e.html\">\"Christianity Today interview: Evangelicals play up 'sexy abstinence' in purity campaigns\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Grand_Rapids_Press\" title=\"The Grand Rapids Press\">The Grand Rapids Press</a></i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">March 21,</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Grand+Rapids+Press&amp;rft.atitle=Christianity+Today+interview%3A+Evangelicals+play+up+%27sexy+abstinence%27+in+purity+campaigns&amp;rft.date=2011-11-12&amp;rft.au=Tanda+Gmiter&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mlive.com%2Fliving%2Fgrand-rapids%2Findex.ssf%2F2011%2F11%2Fchristianity_today_interview_e.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChristine+Gardner\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Hennie Weiss (March 27, 2012). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://metapsychology.mentalhelp.net/poc/view_doc.php?type=book&amp;id=6465\">\"Review - Making Chastity Sexy\"</a>. <i>Metapsychology Online Reviews</i>. <b>16</b> (13)<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">March 21,</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Metapsychology+Online+Reviews&amp;rft.atitle=Review+-+Making+Chastity+Sexy&amp;rft.volume=16&amp;rft.issue=13&amp;rft.date=2012-03-27&amp;rft.au=Hennie+Weiss&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmetapsychology.mentalhelp.net%2Fpoc%2Fview_doc.php%3Ftype%3Dbook%26id%3D6465&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AChristine+Gardner\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw